Package FitnessClassManager

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
FitnessClassManager.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
FitnessClass stores member databases for classes offered to members Includes methods to check in and drop classes
Author:
Arya Shetty, John Greaney-Cheng
